snippet.title: Longplay of Totally Spies!
snippet.description:
Longplay of Totally Spies!, played as the NTSC version on the Game Boy Advance. This game's version was released on Nov. 15th, 2005. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

00:00 - Start
00:49 - The Aptitude Test
10:31 - Save The Earth
19:41 - The Halloween Chase
29:25 - A lovely Singer
40:20 - Kiwi-Kiki In Danger
53:08 - End
53:42 - Credits

By: Terua
